data: The event Product Brainstorm Workshop was organized to generate new product feature ideas.
The event Product Brainstorm Workshop covered icebreaker exercises to encourage creativity among participants.
The event Product Brainstorm Workshop included idea generation sessions during which teams generated over 50 product feature ideas.
The event Product Brainstorm Workshop involved participants voting on the top product feature concepts.
The event Product Brainstorm Workshop had participants forming small groups to flesh out detailed prototype plans for the selected concepts.
The event Product Brainstorm Workshop concluded with a summary of developed prototypes and gathering of feedback for next steps.
